{"tid":905833,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（含語錄）堅決反對一切反含牛鬼蛇神","createTime":"2018-11-17T12:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T12:52:24.000Z","uid":219183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"49d683bbe4dfad852d69e79149f9b37cb2ed6ae2","tid":905833,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:39:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>1.一切反含派都是紙老虎。看起來，反含派的樣子是可怕的，但是實際上並沒有什麼了不起的力量。從長遠的觀點看問題，真正強大的力量不是屬於反含派，而是屬於禾含。<br />\n2.凡是反含反對的，我們就要擁護；凡是反含擁護的，我們就要反對。<br />\n3.凡是鎮壓護含運動的人都沒有好下場！<br />\n4.打反含，分權力</strong><br />\n<br />\n--《含語錄》(節錄)"},{"pid":"e1226b0d472839a7a47f9787e78dec83f82a453a","tid":905833,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:40:07.000Z","msg":"岩, 禾含萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續去交配先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b486976601396d5d0d78265433a4e6e51863a6ee","tid":905833,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1226b0d472839a7a47f9787e78dec83f82a453a","tid":905833,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:40:07.000Z","msg":"岩, 禾含萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續去交配先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:49:59.000Z","msg":"溫熟Sex1001啲notes未<br />\n今次爆3過4無走雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fef66cc564f1d13b03c079bcad472fea5e7e62","tid":905833,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b486976601396d5d0d78265433a4e6e51863a6ee","tid":905833,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1226b0d472839a7a47f9787e78dec83f82a453a","tid":905833,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:40:07.000Z","msg":"岩, 禾含萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼